tutorial: https://docs.oracle.com/javaee/7/tutorial/index.html
newer tutorial: https://jakarta.ee/learn/docs/jakartaee-tutorial/current/index.html

Compile Servlets:
javac -cp "./tomcat/lib/jakarta.servlet-api.jar" -d build AppName/src/ServletName.java

Package into WAR:
jar -cvf OutPutName.war AppName/